# Linux Instructions
General instructions for running Taqo on Linux

## Setup
- Read this: https://github.com/flutter/flutter/wiki/Desktop-shells#tooling
- Switch the the Flutter master channel
```
$ flutter channel master
$ flutter upgrade
```
- Keep the Flutter embedder in sync with [here](https://github.com/google/flutter-desktop-embedding)
```
$ git clone https://github.com/google/flutter-desktop-embedding.git /tmp/embedder
$ cp -R /tmp/embedder/example/linux /path/to/taqo_survey/taqo_client/linux    # Replace if necessary
```

## Running
```
$ cd /path/to/taqo_survey/taqo_client
$ flutter run -d linux
```

